column10:
I recommend for anyone who can get their hand on a VR headset and this game I don't wanna say much because you can't explain you have to show and please do not see spoilers and go head first in the game please I beg you to try.

Gameplay, graphics, soundtrack, plot, everything follows the quality standard of games in the Half-Life seriesl,if you have the opportunity to play this title, I recommend that you play the previous ones to understand the story;

In general, the game is fantastic, I recommend it

It is amazing. I suggest playing this if you have a gaming computer.
I have run into a glitch though ;
if you have drifting controllers, you might just teleport to the wrong location and get flung out of the map.
